Title: Application of a radioreceptor assay in a pharmacokinetic study of oxitropium bromide in healthy volunteers after single i.v., oral and inhalation doses.
Name: Methylscopolamine bromide

Sentece: After i.v. administration the kinetic parameters were: Vc 38.41; t1/2 alpha 5.3 min; t1/2 beta 142 min; AUC 8.9 h.ng.ml-1; renal excretion 50.2%, k10 3.5 l.h-1 and total clearance 1874 ml/min.
